observations/codex/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice.md:77:Loneliness, identity distress, and self-worth chained to private spiritual or scientific verdicts after quiet, blank, or self-loosening states.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice.md:85:Survived critique-mode pressure from Advaita self-luminosity, early Buddhist not-self analysis, predictive-processing level mismatch, prior silence-correction records, and the modern loneliness source.
