observations/codex/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes.md:208:- Build the one-page translation-strain sheet with fields for claim unit, role, ontology, agency, practice aim, authority, verification, what is bent, what is dropped, what is added, and whether role-similarity and repair-similarity survive.
observations/codex/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes.md:209:- If this model is right, then comparisons such as Atman and anatta should show partial role-similarity but repair divergence when authority, verification, and final practice aim are coded. If dual-trained practitioners say the repair is the same after these fields are made explicit, the model is weakened.
