reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-can-boundary-operation-and-custody-rule-be-coded-independently-of-the-ve.md:18:**Steelman:** The strongest version of Claude's idea is that it does not merely compare doctrines such as Atman, sunyata, God, Dao, or no-self. It asks what a practice does with its own authority when its ordinary work reaches a limit. That is a real comparative variable, because direct-recognition traditions, apophatic or dialectical traditions, and embodiment-centered traditions often train different relations to insight, speech, teachers, tests, and reentry. The model also rightly notices that translation strain is not noise: a self-confirming lens can make emptiness look nihilistic, while a self-canceling lens can make witness language look naive.
